that Petter's covering here

00:07:09.132 --> 00:07:11.664
is one of the most
shocking aviation events

00:07:11.664 --> 00:07:13.047
in recent memory.

00:07:13.047 --> 00:07:15.099
And since then,
the preliminary report

00:07:15.099 --> 00:07:15.847
has been released,

00:07:15.847 --> 00:07:18.630
bringing some surprising
and important updates.

